platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: This full-featured powerhouse makes it easy to organize, annotateand edit your PDF library. Import files from your computer or the cloud, then complete forms, add freehand drawings and audio notes and more. On an iPad, revising a PDFs text is as simple as using aword processor, and your original content remains intact. With support for reading files from popular productivity suites, its a convenient way to take the office anywhere you go.
